        "text": "Thou shalt be perfect with the Lord thy God — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Sincerely and wholly his, seeking him and cleaving to him, and to his word alone, and therefore abhorring all commerce and conversations with devils. ",
        "children": []
